INFORMATION CHOICES AND CHANGES
You may opt-out of receiving promotional emails from Webtrends Optimize by following the instructions in
those emails. If you opt-out, we may still send you non-promotional communications, such as emails about
your accounts, product notices, user forum notices or our ongoing business relations.
In some cases, we may not be able to remove your personal information, in which case we will let you know if
we are unable to do so and why.
We will retain your information collected for a commercially reasonable period of time for us to provide
services to you and to use it as stated in this Statement. In addition, we will retain your information for
as long as necessary to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.
Upon request Webtrends Optimize will provide you with information about whether we hold any of your personal
information. You may email
legal@webtrends-optimize.com
to:
request Webtrends Optimize to provide you with information about whether we hold, or process on behalf
